President Muhammadu Buhari in Dubai, on the invitation of His Highness, Sheikh Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum, UAE Vice-President, Prime Minister and Ruler of Dubai, participates in the 9th edition of the Annual Investment Meeting. As a Guest of Honour at this year’s Meeting, Mr. President delivered the Keynote Address, on the theme of the Meeting: “Mapping the Future of Foreign Direct Investment: Enriching World Economies through Digital Globalization.” After his Keynote Address, he took a tour of the Exhibition Stands at the Dubai World Trade Centre, the venue of Annual Meeting. Bashir Ahmad Tanimu is an Online Editor with Africa's Largest TV Network. Produces when not on Social media.